By Anthony Ada Abraham, The game is getting tensed as two of the top housemates, Kiddwaya and Prince have been evicted from the Reality TV Game Show. Prince, Kiddwaya, Dorathy and Ozo were nominated for eviction and it’s been expected that any of them might leave the lockdown edition. Surprisingly, nobody expected Kidd to leave the show, but the fans have spoken. Trikytee winning the head of house and making Laycon is deputy was one of the unexpected event of last week. Also, people were shocked when Vee and Neo weren’t nominated for eviction. In two weeks time, the world would know who would clinch the whooping sum of N85m grand prize. The breakdown of the grand prize for BBNaija season five includes: a N30m cash prize; a two-bedroom apartment courtesy Revolution Plus; a top of the range SUV from Nigerian automaker, Innoson Motors; a trip to Dublin courtesy Guinness; home appliances courtesy Scanfrost; a trip to Dubai packaged by Travelbeta; a year’s supply of Indomie noodles, Munch it and Colgate toothpaste; a year’s supply of Pepsi, a branded chiller and a trip to watch the UEFA Champions League finale; and a brand new Oppo mobile smartphone. 